{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she-- already before that, she was not a youngster anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was a young lady before the war and she studied opera and became a singer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after the war, she became a singer at the German State Opera in East Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was not a top singer, but she always sang, from what my mother told me, supporting roles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my mother tried very hard to get her to come to-- here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She thought she would do very well here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "First of all she had a husband there and also later on a family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was a devout communist, had become a devout communist, and would not leave Eastern Berlin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Adelhaid Muller Hess.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a double name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hess is her maiden name and Muller is her married name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she did meet with my mother in Switzerland once.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have some pictures of her children also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My uncle was in touch with her for a while, but somehow we lost contact and I don't even know what-- it might be interesting to get in touch with her children, but I have no idea what their names are or whether they would have any interest.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I hope I haven't rambled on too much with this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I realize that as a survivor, quote unquote, it's a very-- I sometimes don't feel-- I feel guilty calling myself a survivor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just happened to be there and happened to be at the right place at the right time and haven't been really responsible for my own survival.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the beginning, I mentioned that when we first came to this country, I also had to do what I could to survive in a way.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had all kinds of jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
